title: Alberto, Rangers beat Blue Jays in 14th, lead ALDS 2-0
text:
> Texas Alberto, Rangers beat Blue Jays in 14th, lead ALDS 2-0 Toronto Blue Jays' Josh Donaldson leans on the rail in the dugout during the 11th inning of baseball Game 2 of the American League Division Series against the Texas Rangers in Toronto, Friday, Oct. 9, 2015.
